{"tid":1949364,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"皮膚問題想請教 (有圖)","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T01:36:21.000Z","uid":135878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4693586a400a6c4d4fe7a44440880747d61ea8d","tid":1949364,"uid":135878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"我本身由細到大都好少敏感同冇濕疹<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解之前係外國讀書個陣突然開始生紅點 一開始係肚 會有痕嘅感覺 個陣覺得係比床蝨咬 因為係紅點 而且有叮頭 <br />\n<br />\n但冇幾耐之後返到香港 都冇改善過 而且愈生愈多 而家肚 背脊 身 頸 連胳肋底都有紅點一達達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有啲就有叮頭 有啲就齋紅點 上網睇症狀好似一樣叫風瘙癢嘅皮膚敏感<br />\n<br />\n因為而家仲隔離緊未睇醫生 所以托屋企人去買中藥 食完有好咗 而家啲紅點開始轉暗 而且叮頭部份有啲甩皮 但咁樣好似會留印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴絲知道究竟係咩嚟 好痕 但又未去到好辛苦 但隔離緊所以真係要等完咗先睇到醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有巴絲試過風瘙癢 請同我講係咪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者其他敏感<br />\n知道點去印都好 麻煩同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身皮膚唔錯而家好似會留好多暗嘅印 唔知去唔去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZwQRav.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZwQRav.png&h=2aeb908e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba3b069084606032bd655d4ff872e1949db5ae77","tid":1949364,"uid":135878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ebd448948ec7eba23fdb08072280e7117182c9","tid":1949364,"uid":135878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe7ce59e923722e8ff10d29f09380f2de113678","tid":1949364,"uid":135878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98ebb383a02f698368803bbb9adbdea5037c941","tid":1949364,"uid":345761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"風癩應該唔會留印 俾蟲咬就會 會唔會係你帶咗啲蝨返屋企？帶返黎嘅衫有冇洗乾淨？"},{"pid":"b023c9247128af6923af981a47e798eba75092b0","tid":1949364,"uid":135878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b98ebb383a02f698368803bbb9adbdea5037c941","tid":1949364,"uid":345761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"風癩應該唔會留印 俾蟲咬就會 會唔會係你帶咗啲蝨返屋企？帶返黎嘅衫有冇洗乾淨？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:27:15.000Z","msg":"應該唔會 因為一入屋企門口就去沖涼 衫直接放入洗衣機 所以都唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a379c1ffc1425f6c20e72255621d5f8bacf38fe4","tid":1949364,"uid":254813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"呢d情況d啡印應該係皮膚過敏導致痕跟住你R就會形成。我都有，情況唔嚴重但一到轉天氣尤其轉乾就會出現，反反覆覆！"},{"pid":"b2c5d432478c20859b6a5f8c27ad01353604c453","tid":1949364,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"最好唔好R(雖然R完好治愈)，多補濕。唯有等天氣轉定就慢慢好，印會退。大約夏天時間。"}]}